N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1221.3 - Entry upon court and roof areas restricted

State Regulations

The occupant shall not enter upon any court or roof area
(including parking area) unless specifically so authorized by lease, permit, license or other agreement with the Port Authority. Notes
